## ğŸ…¿ğŸ…°ğŸ…½ğŸ…´ğŸ†‚
set-option -g pane-base-index 1     # set first pane to index 1 (not 0) to map more to the keyboard layout
bind-key q kill-pane                # kill pane without confirmation (comment is incorrect)
bind -n M-c kill-pane \; select-layout      # kill pane and auto-adjust layout
bind -n M-n split-window \; select-layout   # create new pane and auto-adjust layout
